>> source: https://deliciouslittlebites.com/garlic-rice/
>> total time: 30 minutes
>> serves: 4

Melt the @butter{1%Tbsp} in a #medium saucepan{} over medium heat.

Add the @garlic{6%cloves} and cook, stirring frequently, for ~{1%minute}.

Add the @jasmine rice{1%cup} and stir to coat in the garlic butter.

Pour in the @water{1.5%cups} and season with @salt{}. Bring to a boil, cover, reduce heat to low and simmer until tender, about 15 to ~{20%minutes).
